"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) showing academic major distributions across divisions and departments. Clicking an AS/EN division filters View 2 to show minor enrollment patterns in that division. A bar click in View 2 drills down to department-level details that affect View 4's outlier highlighting. Simultaneously, View 3's advisor-minor division heatmap responds to View 1 selections, completing the analysis of academic/extracurricular correlations."